OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfcom orders phone networks
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto block foreign scam calls
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Major phone networks have agreed to    
OL,6, automatically block almost all internet
OL,7, calls coming from abroad if they       
OL,8, pretend to be from UK numbers, Ofcom   
OL,9, has confirmed.                         
OL,11,FCriminals have been using              
OL,12,Finternet-based calling technology to   
OL,13,Fmake it look like a phone call or text 
OL,14,Fis coming from a real telephone number.
OL,16,FAlmost 45 million consumers were       
OL,17,Ftargeted by phone scams this summer.   
OL,19,FOfcom said it expected the measures to 
OL,20,Fbe introduced at pace as a "priority". 
